common_issues.title: Pieces Core Services Fails to Open Due to WebSocket Error
common_issues.description: Multiple users across macOS and Windows are unable to open Pieces Core Services.  The error is a WebSocketException with a 404 HTTP status code, indicating the service is not running or accessible at the expected endpoint (http://127.0.0.1:39300). Check if Pieces Core Services is running, verify firewall settings, and ensure the correct port is being used.

The connection to 'http://127.0.0.1:39300/user/last_checked_in/stream#' failed to upgrade to websocket.  Potential solutions include checking Pieces Core Services installation, network connectivity, and firewall settings. Ensure the service is running and the port is accessible.
